      "settings": {
        "tagline": "The Story Behind the Soap",
        "heading_line1": "A son's promise.",
        "heading_line2_normal": "A father's",
        "heading_line2_italic": "dream of purity.",
        "body_text": "My father, Abhay Manik Birla, didn't just see saffron as a business. He saw it as a legacy. He dreamed of a soap that didn't just smell like a memory — but actually carried the living benefit of the saffron he loved so much.",
        "quote": "Every time a bar of Senfa leaves our hands, I feel like I'm finally finishing that conversation with my Dad.",
        "body_text_2": "In 2023, that dream became our inheritance. From rich Himalayan saffron fields to your morning ritual — this is the purity he always wanted you to have.",
        "cta_label": "Read the Complete Story",
        "cta_url": "shopify://pages/our-story",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/kashmir.jpg",
        "caption": "Abhay Manik Birla · 1940–2013",
